Coming this <i>Kwanzaa.</i>

2403
01:36:49.801 --> 01:36:51.203
(CROW CAWS)

2404
01:38:02.975 --> 01:38:06.378
Cuckoo. Cuckoo.

2405
01:38:07.113 --> 01:38:10.382
Happy Birthday. A.S. Berger.

2406
01:38:10.482 --> 01:38:13.318
Something isn't right here.
SHORTHAND: Happy birthday...

2407
01:38:13.418 --> 01:38:15.387
He's definitely Ghostface.

2408
01:38:15.955 --> 01:38:16.889
Sit.

2409
01:38:17.857 --> 01:38:19.424
I agree. Berger.

2410
01:38:19.524 --> 01:38:21.560
That hand should spend
the rest of its life in prison.

2411
01:38:21.660 --> 01:38:23.628
That little hand. man. I mean--

2412
01:38:23.729 --> 01:38:27.365
Respectfully. that thing would
probably give a nice handjob.

2413
01:38:27.466 --> 01:38:29.836
Off the chain. guaranteed.

2414
01:38:29.936 --> 01:38:31.037
Tight grip.

2415
01:38:31.137 --> 01:38:32.337
Make your meat
look two times bigger.

2416
01:38:32.437 --> 01:38:33.538
(CHUCKLES) Yeah.

2417
01:38:33.638 --> 01:38:35.041
I don't want
a handjob from him.

2418
01:38:35.141 --> 01:38:36.408
Let me tell you that.
first and foremost.

2419
01:38:36.508 --> 01:38:38.510
I do not want a handjob.
Me neither.

2420
01:38:38.610 --> 01:38:41.313
However. when you look at it.
like a shotgun--

2421
01:38:41.413 --> 01:38:43.348
(CLICKS. PUFFS) You're done.
(SHOTGUN COCKS. FIRES)

2422
01:38:43.448 --> 01:38:44.716
(MIMICS EXPLOSION)

2423
01:38:44.816 --> 01:38:46.351
Now. listen.
we're gonna hold him. okay?

2424
01:38:46.451 --> 01:38:48.087
Okay.
It might be a day.

2425
01:38:48.187 --> 01:38:49.354
two weeks. I don't know.

2426
01:38:49.454 --> 01:38:50.555
I don't know how long
this movie is.

2427
01:38:50.655 --> 01:38:52.691
Like a Chris Nolan movie
with farts.

2428
01:38:52.791 --> 01:38:55.228
But what I want you to do
is go in there

2429
01:38:55.327 --> 01:38:57.329
and show him what you got.

2430
01:38:57.429 --> 01:38:59.165
Cock it and rock it.

2431
01:38:59.264 --> 01:39:01.533
(DISTANT SIRENS WAILING)

2432
01:39:02.334 --> 01:39:03.568
Ah.
(DOOR UNLOCKS)

2433
01:39:05.104 --> 01:39:07.672
(GASPS) Oh!
(DOOR SHUTS)

2434
01:39:08.306 --> 01:39:10.143
SHORTHAND:
There she is.

2435
01:39:10.243 --> 01:39:12.544
The birthday girl.

2436
01:39:15.514 --> 01:39:16.815
I brought a cake.

2437
01:39:18.117 --> 01:39:19.518
Make a wish.

2438
01:39:21.087 --> 01:39:23.022
My germs!
(SPUTTERS)

2439
01:39:23.122 --> 01:39:24.556
(SPUTTERS)

2440
01:39:24.656 --> 01:39:26.424
(BERGER SPITS)
(SMACKS LIPS)

2441
01:39:26.525 --> 01:39:29.095
Finger-licking good.
(GIGGLES)

2442
01:39:29.195 --> 01:39:33.298
Agent Berger. I'm just trying
to give you my strong hand.

2443
01:39:33.398 --> 01:39:35.201
No!
But it's a meme.

2444
01:39:35.300 --> 01:39:39.504
Mr. Shorthand.
are you Ghostface?

2445
01:39:39.604 --> 01:39:41.974
(WHOOPS) Here we go--
(GRUNTS. WHIMPERS)

2446
01:39:42.074 --> 01:39:44.911
Whew. that stings.
It's sort of--

2447
01:39:45.011 --> 01:39:45.945
(THUDS)
Whoo.

2448
01:39:46.045 --> 01:39:47.579
Okay. that hurts.
Stop.

2449
01:39:47.679 --> 01:39:49.015
Can I talk to you
for a second?

2450
01:39:49.115 --> 01:39:50.782
Yeah. o-okay.

2451
01:39:50.883 --> 01:39:52.450
(THUDS)
(MOANS. GASPS)

2452
01:39:52.551 --> 01:39:54.153
This table needs an airbag.

2453
01:39:54.253 --> 01:39:55.121
It should-- (GRUNTS)

2454
01:39:55.221 --> 01:39:56.889
BOTH: Goddamn!

2455
01:39:56.989 --> 01:39:58.191
Whoo!

2456
01:39:58.291 --> 01:39:59.658
I didn't think it would
hurt so bad.

2457
01:39:59.758 --> 01:40:03.095
So we got the wrong guy.
Could have told you that.

2458
01:40:03.196 --> 01:40:04.663
Why?
'Cause I'm psychic.

2459
01:40:04.763 --> 01:40:06.833
(SHORTHAND GASPS)
Oh. yeah!

2460
01:40:06.933 --> 01:40:08.100
You know. it's what--

2461
01:40:08.201 --> 01:40:09.467
(THUDS)
BOTH: Oh. shit!

2462
01:40:09.568 --> 01:40:11.137
(SIGHS) Oh. God.
that's how I feel.

2463
01:40:11.237 --> 01:40:12.939
Let me tell you some--
(GRUNTS)

2464
01:40:13.039 --> 01:40:15.174
What do we do now?

2465
01:40:15.274 --> 01:40:16.808
Back out slowly.
(THUDDING CONTINUES)

2466
01:40:16.909 --> 01:40:18.610
Like my neighbor when
I caught him inside my wife.

2467
01:40:18.710 --> 01:40:20.313
SHORTHAND:
Where are you guys going?

2468
01:40:20.412 --> 01:40:21.513
(THUDS. SHORTHAND GROANS)
They're still together?

2469
01:40:21.613 --> 01:40:23.216
(THUDS)
Unfortunately.

2470
01:40:23.316 --> 01:40:24.482
SHORTHAND: Ow!
(THUDS)

2471
01:40:24.583 --> 01:40:26.551
Sorry. man.
It's okay.

2472
01:40:26.651 --> 01:40:28.087
We're a throuple now.
(SHORTHAND GROANS)

2473
01:40:28.187 --> 01:40:29.487
(THUDS)
